summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2006 TOYOTA SIENNA. WHILE DRIVING 25 MPH, THE VEHICLE STALLED AND THE AIR BAG AND BRAKE WARNING INDICATORS ILLUMINATED. THE CONTACT HEARD AN ABNORMAL BEEPING NOISE. THE LOCAL DEALER WAS NOT CONTACTED. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT DIAGNOSED OR REPAIRED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT NOTIFIED. THE VIN WAS UNKNOWN. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 143,332.
